SerializableSliceSizingRuleImpl
public class SliceSizingRuleImpl
extends SliceSizingRule

Implementation of SliceSizingRule. It is recommended that a Serializable subclass be used instead of this class, such as SerializableSliceSizingRuleImpl, and that only Serializable subclasses of Member be used, such as SerializableMember. If an instance of this class is used in conjunction with session change management, it is subject to being replaced by an equivalent instance of SerializableSliceSizingRuleImpl.
